### Create property #2
POST http://localhost:3000/properties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Lakeside Cottage",
  "city": "Austin",
  "monthly_rent": 2200,
  "bedrooms": 3
}

### Create property #3
POST http://localhost:3000/properties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Downtown Loft",
  "city": "Dallas",
  "monthly_rent": 1800,
  "bedrooms": 1
}

### Update property #1
PATCH http://localhost:3000/properties/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Lakeside Cottage",
  "city": "Austin",
  "monthly_rent": 2400,
  "bedrooms": 3,
  "is_available": false
}

### Update property that does not exist
PATCH http://localhost:3000/properties/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Missing Property",
  "city": "Nowhere"
}

### Delete property #1
DELETE http://localhost:3000/properties/4

